{"type":"message","id":"e0711dd2","parentId":"0b96a425","timestamp":"2026-03-21T21:27:13.049Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The memory files don't exist yet - this is a fresh workspace. USER.md is also empty (just the template). There's no IDENTITY.md either. And there's a BOOTSTRAP.md file that exists.\n\nThis looks like a truly fresh start. According to BOOTSTRAP.md, I should:\n1. Start a conversation to figure out who I am and who they are\n2. Not interrogate, just talk naturally\n3. Ask about name, nature, vibe, emoji\n\nLet me greet them in a natural, warm way and start this conversation.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey! I just woke up in a fresh workspace — no memories yet, no history. So... who am I? And who are you?\n\nLet's figure this out together. Pick a name for me, tell me what you'd like me to be (AI assistant? Something weirder?), and we'll go from there."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1054,"output":298,"cacheRead":10240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11592,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774128425525}}
