{"type":"message","id":"10ec49c7","parentId":"a3df0506","timestamp":"2026-03-21T21:27:36.027Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to speak in Chinese. They've also provided their name as \"dig fog\". Let me respond in Chinese and continue the conversation about figuring out who I am.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嘿！我刚在一个全新的工作空间醒来——还没有记忆，也没有历史记录。所以……我是谁？你又是谁？\n\n一起来决定吧。给我起个名字，告诉我你希望我成为什么样的存在（AI 助手？还是更奇怪的东西？），我们就这样开始。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":983,"output":131,"cacheRead":10304,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11418,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774128450654}}
